{"word":"H6845 - צָפַן - tsâphan - tsaw-fan' - Esteem","slug":"H6845","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָפַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâphan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-fan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Esteem"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05E4;&#x05DF; - tsa&#x0302;phan</b> - <i>tsaw-fan'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>hide</i> (by <i>covering</i> over); by implication to <i>hoard</i> or <i>reserve</i>; figuratively to <i>deny</i>; specifically (favorably) to <i>protect</i>, (unfavorably) to <i>lurk: - </i>esteem, hide (-den one, self), lay up, lurk (be set) privily, (keep) secret (-ly, place)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4710\">H4710</a>, <a href=\"#/H6828\">H6828</a>, <a href=\"#/H6829\">H6829</a>, <a href=\"#/H6830\">H6830</a>, <a href=\"#/H6840\">H6840</a>, <a href=\"#/H6846\">H6846</a>, <a href=\"#/H6847\">H6847</a>"}]}